Dear HEVGA members,

Only one week left to register for the biggest in-person student game jam. Please share with your students, we have mentors from major game companies, like EA<https://www.facebook.com/EA/?ref=gs&__tn__=%2CdK-R-R&eid=ARBVANyewS0aMLTM6m_bbmyYwQQ3tpMSeaSPzkGR42YRgGQYzivW0e2ZOhl9VyU4RmdEReWD1m0EF9mK&fref=gs&dti=390633317808066&hc_location=group>, BioWare<https://www.facebook.com/BioWare/?ref=gs&__tn__=%2CdK-R-R&eid=ARACmIBt5DTChmiMY-SZbg-Y0ZRmk4O9urh9aJg_EGeXXTtVXpdCMK4BZFrNxr1qlgWArD7MQg9XUWs8&fref=gs&dti=390633317808066&hc_location=group>, Insomniac Games<https://www.facebook.com/insomniacgames/?ref=gs&__tn__=%2CdK-R-R&eid=ARBI5f8yjgzRzCOqpS_wOZedmVa885HwBhrTwdPjmiNNk4YwvuXcyi1Q8Kz7AykGJgrtrdjVMQT_rq7Z&fref=gs&dti=390633317808066&hc_location=group>, Amazon<https://www.facebook.com/Amazon/?ref=gs&__tn__=%2CdK-R-R&eid=ARD8uaRYyAy2r0GkOJa74JM-nwguQf8oBvZlYEa0_5Fm5GirbJgcPlbGI0LwtJDegApBygI_vKWONd7W&fref=gs&dti=390633317808066&hc_location=group>, BluePoint Games<https://www.facebook.com/Bluepoint-Games-196082807117165/?ref=gs&__tn__=%2CdK-R-R&eid=ARDTqK9z_iqDx_4QFJafY4q1nKHcBeAwgOFRD76iH5W3RTdQRjAiDyD1xMebANgoY7vVZr39hWsfKMFz&fref=gs&dti=390633317808066&hc_location=group>, Unity, EPIC to name but a few, all helping students for the whole weekend.
No experience necessary for the students, there will be workshops by Unity and EPIC before the jam. We have teams from all over the US and 2 teams from China. Great food, great prizes and lots of fun. [Registration Link<https://secure.touchnet.com/C21490_ustores/web/classic/product_detail.jsp?PRODUCTID=7426>]

cheers

Andr

-- 
